<h1>Display options</h1>

<p>At the bottom of the preferences page are the display options.  These allow you to control how the Intranet looks and what information is displayed in the &ldquo;intraboxes&rdquo;&mdash;the panels displayed down the left side of the page.</p>

<strong>Themes:</strong>
<p>Themes change the appearance of the whole Intranet.  To change your theme, click the &ldquo;Style&rdquo; drop-down menu and select a different theme.</p>
