<strong>Intraboxes:</strong>
<p>Intraboxes are a way to quickly access Intranet functions from any page.  They live in the sidebar on the left side of the page.  To add or remove intraboxes, scroll to the bottom of the preferences page.  To add an intrabox, select it from the right-side menu and click the left-pointing arrow.  To remove one, select it from the left-side menu and click the right-pointing arrow.  To reorder your intraboxes, just drag them up and down in the sidebar.  You can also rearrange, minimize, or remove intraboxes using the controls at the top-right of each box.</p>
